《'''史蒂夫·乔布斯传'''》（{{lang-en|''Steve Jobs''}}）是[[史蒂夫·乔布斯|史蒂夫·乔布斯]]授权[[CNN|CNN]]和《[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]》前高管[[沃尔特·艾萨克森|沃尔特·艾萨克森]]撰写的[[传记|传记]]，艾萨克森曾写过[[本杰明·富兰克林|本杰明·富兰克林]]和[[阿尔伯特·爱因斯坦|阿尔伯特·爱因斯坦]]的传记。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2391112,00.asp|title=Tell-All Steve Jobs Biography Hits Stores on November 21|last=Yin|first=Sara|date=2011-08-15|publisher=[[PC_Magazine|PC Magazine]]|accessdate=2011-10-06|archive-date=2017-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170114085059/http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2391112,00.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/08/15/steve-jobs-biography-cover-photo-and-november-release-date_n_927548.html|title=Steve Jobs Biography Gets Cover, November Release Date|last=Gilbert|first=Jason|date=2011-08-25|publisher=[[赫芬顿邮报|The Huffington Post]]|accessdate=2011-10-06|archive-date=2012-08-31|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AKPatTOr?url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/08/15/steve-jobs-biography-cover-photo-and-november-release-date_n_927548.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在两年多的时间里，艾萨克森对乔布斯本人进行了40多次采访，再加上对乔布斯的100多位家人、朋友、对手、竞争对手和同事的采访，艾萨克森全面了解乔布斯的一生。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://tech.fortune.cnn.com/2011/08/16/a-peek-at-steve-jobs-book-jacket-front-and-back/|title=A peek at Steve Jobs' book jacket – front, back and spine|last=Elmer-DeWitt|first=Philip|date=2011-08-16|work=[[财富_(杂志)|Fortune]]|publisher={{tsl|en|CNN Money||CNN Money}}|accessdate=2011-10-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111016054137/http://tech.fortune.cnn.com/2011/08/16/a-peek-at-steve-jobs-book-jacket-front-and-back/|archivedate=2011-10-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref>据说乔布斯鼓励被采访的人真实地讲述故事。乔布斯对这本书除了封面以外，对书的内容没有任何控制权，并放弃了在出版前阅读这本书的权利。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/technology/2011/08/steve-jobs-a-biography-gets-earlier-nov-21-release-date.html|title='Steve Jobs: A Biography' release date is moved up to Nov. 21|last=Olivarez-Giles|first=Nathan|date=2011-08-15|work=[[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]]|accessdate=2011-10-06|archive-date=2012-08-31|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AKPX6Ikg?url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/technology/2011/08/steve-jobs-a-biography-gets-earlier-nov-21-release-date.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2011年10月24日，乔布斯去世19天后，美国[[西蒙與舒斯特|西蒙與舒斯特]]出版公司出版了这本书。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Biography of Apple CEO Steve Jobs to arrive in November|url=http://www.appleinsider.com/articles/11/08/15/biography_of_apple_ceo_steve_jobs_to_arrive_in_november.html|accessdate=2011-10-06|date=2011-08-15|last=Ong|first=Josh|publisher={{tsl|en|AppleInsider||AppleInsider}}|archive-date=2012-08-31|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AKPYJVdL?url=http://www.appleinsider.com/articles/11/08/15/biography_of_apple_ceo_steve_jobs_to_arrive_in_november.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>简体中文版由[[中信出版社|中信出版社]]出版，<ref>{{Cite web|title=《乔布斯传》中文版授权始末|url=https://tech.qq.com/a/20111031/000002.htm|accessdate=|author=|date=2011-10-31|format=|publisher=北京商报|language=|via=腾讯科技|archive-date=2012-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120905115846/http://tech.qq.com/a/20111031/000002.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>繁体中文版由[[天下文化|天下文化]]出版。2013年9月11日，繁体中文版推出增訂版；2014年3月1日，简体中文版推出修订版。

2015年10月9日，由[[艾倫·索金|艾倫·索金]]编剧、[[丹尼·鮑伊|丹尼·鮑伊]]执导、[[麥可·法斯賓達|麥可·法斯賓達]]主演的[[史帝夫賈伯斯_(電影)|同名电影]]上映。

== 外观 ==
=== 封面 ===
本书初版封面使用的是{{tsl|en|Albert Watson (photographer)|阿尔伯特·沃森}}在2006年为《[[财富_(杂志)|财富]]》杂志拍摄的一张乔布斯的照片。沃森用了三个小时的时间来设置他的拍照设备，乔布斯到达摄影棚的时候没有马上看沃森，而是看了看他的设备，然后对沃森的{{tsl|en|Large format (photography)||4×5相机}}说：“哇，你在拍电影啊”。<ref name="Steve Jobs: Visionary, Inventor, and Very Challenging Photo Subject">{{Cite web|title=Steve Jobs: Visionary, Inventor, and Very Challenging Photo Subject|url=http://pdnpulse.pdnonline.com/2011/10/steve-jobs-visionary-inventor-and-very-challenging-photo-subject.html|accessdate=2015-10-03|date=2011-10-06|last=Walker|first=David|work={{tsl|en|Photo District News||Photo District News}}|publisher=[[尼爾森NV|Nielsen]]|archive-date=2019-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402103656/https://pdnpulse.pdnonline.com/2011/10/steve-jobs-visionary-inventor-and-very-challenging-photo-subject.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

{{Quotation|If you look at that shot, you can see the intensity. It was my intention that by looking at him, that you knew this guy was smart. I heard later that it was his favorite photograph of all time.<br />如果你看到那张照片，你可以看它的韵味。我拍摄时候想的是，当你看到乔布斯的这张照片，你就知道他很聪明。后来我听说这是他最喜欢的照片。|{{tsl|en|Albert Watson (photographer)|阿尔伯特·沃森|}}<ref name="Steve Jobs: Visionary, Inventor, and Very Challenging Photo Subject" />}}

乔布斯给了沃森一个小时的的拍摄时间，比他给大多数摄影师的拍摄时间都要长。据报道，沃森曾要求乔布斯95%，甚至100%的时间都要对着镜头看，思考下一个摆在你面前的项目，还要想想别人对他提出的挑战。<ref name="Steve Jobs: Visionary, Inventor, and Very Challenging Photo Subject" />

英文版封面的字体为[[Helvetica|Helvetica]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Biography of Apple CEO Steve Jobs to arrive in November|url=http://www.appleinsider.com/articles/11/08/15/biography_of_apple_ceo_steve_jobs_to_arrive_in_november.html|accessdate=2011-10-16|date=2011-08-15|last=Ong|first=Josh|publisher={{tsl|en|AppleInsider||AppleInsider}}|archive-date=2012-08-31|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AKPYJVdL?url=http://www.appleinsider.com/articles/11/08/15/biography_of_apple_ceo_steve_jobs_to_arrive_in_november.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

